        "content": "<p>I'm currently working on formalizing the exercises from Jay Cummings' \"Real Analysis\" book. You can find my progress so far on GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/tautastic/real-analysis\">Real Analysis Exercises Repository</a>.</p>\n<p>Feel free to check it out. Contributions are welcome!</p>",
